content:
When you use Data Cloud reports and dashboards, your data is stored and processed in Data Cloud. Using Data Cloud features for reports and dashboards has billing implications.

Data Cloud services and usage impacts the consumption of credits used for billing. Usage types include:

Data Queries - calculated based on records processed
Real-Time Profile API - calculated based on records processed

For more information, refer to your contract or contact your account executive.
title: Data Cloud Billing for Reports and Dashboards
